Red Bull triumphs in Formula 1 with a secret weapon from Siemens
Software proposes improvements in real-time vehicles.
Since Red Bull came into Formula 1 series in 2004, his history in this extraordinary world of speed has been characterized by surprise and success.
At first, no one took too seriously the possibilities of this new incoming team, and despite the rising trend in recent times, they all settled on the Ferrari Fernanda Alonsa triumph.
